                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Whether you have clicky invis or the spell memmed.  During the cast time of invis you can change targets and it will still invis you.
<br />

<br />
So..
<br />

<br />
Cast invis (spell or clickie)
<br />
During cast.. target pet that will break and run at you
<br />
Root/mez ~ whatever np
<br />

<br />
Just a suggestion for those who like to break charm with invis like me.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Jermz
